{"tid":1353312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察(公安)喺黑社會面前已經抬唔起頭做人","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:48:31.000Z","uid":273207,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6aeb85c0f9ae38ad4e3011abc7c153ca12acb83","tid":1353312,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"經過尋日(22日)元朗同周邊地區癱瘓<br />\n好明顯見到市民已經對警察完全失去信心<br />\n<br />\n當放風話元朗會搞事時<br />\n警察都唔肯承諾會保障市民安全<br />\n而係靠大家自己早收工收檔黎自保<br />\n<br />\n班警察仲以為自己好威威<br />\n實質係佢地喺黑社會面前已經抬唔起頭，要幫佢含同奶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，下次見到警察唔應該話<br />\n「警黑勾結」<br />\n而係話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「警察係黑社會既狗」(死黑狗)</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">擒賊先擒王</span></strong>，警犬只係黑社會既狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>上環<span style=\"color: red;\">無示警開槍</span></strong></span>亦都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府</strong></span>order<br />\n(雖然班死黑狗都水平開槍都好撚仆街)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span>先係重點，講完！"},{"pid":"710e6a577ec91a8206fdbdab72d7b11860aff2ee","tid":1353312,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01520e42f3fc12672351775054e95045a87b78e0","tid":1353312,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21af899f6c0e9d98fdbe6f87ec171c71ec7da2fc","tid":1353312,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"班警狗連黑社會都不如"},{"pid":"27dfb522fd41bc0410b0e485249d89ffe4aebd2